{"tid":299367,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有命出返嚟！93歲黑幫頭目判囚8年 100歲成功出獄","createTime":"2017-06-27T04:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T05:40:45.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"207ea29dede08d81ed3b5c3e975eece5507d4d16","tid":299367,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:42:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498377894_d487.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498377894_d487.jpg&h=8c233996&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n美國紐約五大黑幫家族之一、科隆博（Colombo）的「二當家」弗蘭傑斯（John Franzese）在93歲時被判囚8年，當時律師求情指他年邁又多病，判較長年期「毫無意義」，但法官不理判他監禁8年，想不到他捱過這段時間，100歲刑滿出獄，成為聯邦監獄系統最老的囚犯。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498377904_f258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498377904_f258.jpg&h=e6932143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170626/56873817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170626%2F56873817&d=%2BU4DPnDw0U%2F5gYyF12vnWcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=8d438768\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170626%2F56873817&h=8821dad7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170626/56873817</a></div><br />\n<br />\n弗蘭傑斯周五獲釋，他看來精神不錯，面帶笑容。他在93歲時因以威脅手段，迫曼哈頓一間脫衣舞俱樂部交錢，被判囚8年；當局估計他過去曾殺害50至100人。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦助理檢察官波薩（Cristina Posa）在法官判刑前曾表示，監禁時間不應太短，「讓他在獄中坐牢至死也不為過&hellip;&hellip;他要為過去一個世紀美化黑手黨負上主要責任。」弗蘭傑斯的黑幫生活的確「多姿多采」，例如經常與名人來往，旅遊行樂。不過弗蘭傑斯的律師反駁，指當事人年事已高，加上有腎臟、心臟等問題，判刑太久也沒有意義。<br />\n<br />\n法官最終決定判刑8年，強調這是要向公眾表達「你永遠無法逃避畢生參與有組織犯罪的後果」。<br />\n<br />\n弗蘭傑斯自19歲開始作奸犯科，因襲擊罪被捕；當兵時也因暴力問題，在1942年被逐走。2010年因勒索及其他罪行被判罪成，連自己兒子也轉做污點證人指控他。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498377955_4331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498377955_4331.jpg&h=1ce3fbd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">弗蘭傑斯（圖中）年輕時照片(互聯網)</span></div><br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約郵報》"},{"pid":"b544411ca37e1c3da8fea7a6764d0c8470a601c0","tid":299367,"uid":40450,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:43:37.000Z","msg":"真正100歲唔死都有新聞"},{"pid":"a8cd1971403d8f2c40803da351e50ca486cce509","tid":299367,"uid":18430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:45:30.000Z","msg":"有冇黑幫片推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c181d91b5b1b8f398af44ce214c58f66d2971fb","tid":299367,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:46:28.000Z","msg":"God father <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4891659536850f2b7cdfa6bf0c800f157a7423b","tid":299367,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"godfather"},{"pid":"c6224e3a1014153212d1d7e4213a4de35725d04c","tid":299367,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真正100歲唔死都有新聞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc6e7bb5a90423e737acef7fd6b1a64898b0ec8","tid":299367,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"叫聲大佬"},{"pid":"4ad7d71cdaf1cc4c56408a93afde5ffc29befeb2","tid":299367,"uid":498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"93歲仲要出黎收保護費， 似乎黑幫呢盤生意唔易做"},{"pid":"92b479854ea13f8d2f841995dfe42c1d973d7384","tid":299367,"uid":1300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"93+8=100?"},{"pid":"475c050ea19dc898ac8a7f53ef1592e127c174a3","tid":299367,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>93+8=100?</blockquote><br />\n扣假期"}]}